    "26524272": {
      "title": "p21 in cancer: intricate networks and multiple activities",
      "abstract": "p21 has a well-known role in mediating p53-induced growth arrest. However, this protein can affect many other cellular functions and is activated independently of p53. What are the p53-independent roles of p21 in cancer, and could p21 be a therapeutic target?"
